snippet.title: 3 Skulls of the Toltecs gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for 3 Skulls of the Toltecs, Dos PC game produced by Revistronic in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/3-skulls-of-the-toltecs/7287/
The game is a humorous adventure graphic where you play the role of a cowboy in the far west..
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
